Package: ReportGenerator
Type: Package
Title: Automatic Report Generator of Darwin EU Studies
Version: 1.10.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Cesar", "Barboza", , "c.barboza@darwin-eu.org", role = c("cre", "aut"), comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0002-4453-3071")),
    person("Ger", "Inberg", , "g.inberg@darwin-eu.org", role = "aut")
  )
Description: The goal of this package is to generate automatic reports in Word format of DARWIN study results. It includes a Shiny interface and accepts data from the IncidencePrevalence, DrugUtilisation and TreatmentPatterns packages. 
